Found the problem in "ClusterEndpoint.java" where in "migrateInstances()" we throw an exception when the lookup fails for the first cluster causing us to go out of the loop and never try the second cluster.

{code}
public MigrateInstancesResponseType migrateInstances( final MigrateInstancesType request ) throws EucalyptusCloudException {
[...]
      for ( ServiceConfiguration ccConfig : Topology.enabledServices( ClusterController.class ) ) {
        try {
          ServiceConfiguration node = Nodes.lookup( ccConfig, request.getSourceHost( ) );//found the node!
          [...]
        } catch ( EucalyptusCloudException ex ) {
          throw ex;
        } catch ( NoSuchElementException ex ) {
          throw new EucalyptusCloudException( "Failed to find ENABLED cluster for node " + request.getSourceHost( ), ex );
        } catch ( Exception ex ) {
          LOG.error( ex );
          throw new EucalyptusCloudException( "Migrating off of node " + request.getSourceHost( ) + " failed because of: " + ex.getMessage( ), ex );
        }
    }
    [...]
}
{code}

{code}
diff --git a/clc/modules/cluster-manager/src/main/java/com/eucalyptus/cluster/ClusterEndpoint.java b/clc/modules/cluster-manager/src/main/java/com/eucalyptus/cluster/ClusterEndpoint.java
index e718c1c..940bd54 100644
--- a/clc/modules/cluster-manager/src/main/java/com/eucalyptus/cluster/ClusterEndpoint.java
+++ b/clc/modules/cluster-manager/src/main/java/com/eucalyptus/cluster/ClusterEndpoint.java
@@ -163,7 +163,7 @@ public class ClusterEndpoint implements Startable {
         } catch ( EucalyptusCloudException ex ) {
           throw ex;
         } catch ( NoSuchElementException ex ) {
-          throw new EucalyptusCloudException( "Failed to find ENABLED cluster for node " + request.getSourceHost( ), ex );
+               // Ignore and continue
         } catch ( Exception ex ) {
           LOG.error( ex );
           throw new EucalyptusCloudException( "Migrating off of node " + request.getSourceHost( ) + " failed because of: " + ex.getMessage( ), ex );
{code}
